#. TRANSLATORS: This is the name of a starting condition
#: addons/basic-outpost.wad/addon:4 addons/basic-outpost.wad/amazons.lua:11
#: addons/basic-outpost.wad/atlanteans.lua:11
#: addons/basic-outpost.wad/barbarians.lua:11
